---
// About.astro — Devon + Reality Knights origin story
---

<section class="py-24 px-6" id="about">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">

    <div class="mb-14">
      <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted text-xs tracking-[0.25em] uppercase mb-3 font-medium">
        The person behind it
      </p>
      <h2
        class="font-outfit text-rk-text leading-tight"
        style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 700;"
      >
        Devon Lambert
      </h2>
    </div>

    <!-- Photo + bio layout -->
    <div class="about-layout">

      <!-- Photo column -->
      <div class="about-photo-col">
        <div class="about-photo-wrap">
          <img
            src="/devon.jpg"
            alt="Devon Lambert"
            class="about-photo"
          />
          <!-- Accent glow ring -->
          <div class="about-photo-glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text column -->
      <div class="about-text-col">

        <!-- Bio block -->
        <div class="about-block">
          <div class="about-accent-bar" style="background: #06B6D4;"></div>
          <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
            Devon Lambert started gaming at 8 years old on a NES and never really stopped.
            He's completed the entire Final Fantasy franchise, gone deep on Bleach, DBZ, and
            Demon Slayer — and at some point started practicing breathing techniques from the latter.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Philosophy block -->
        <div class="about-block">
          <div class="about-accent-bar" style="background: #7C3AED;"></div>
          <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem;">
            Reality Knights is the holding company for what happens when someone like that
            also gets serious about markets, AI, and building things people actually want.
            Each venture starts with conviction — a clear problem, a real audience, and a
            reason to exist.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Origin story block — full width -->
    <div class="about-block about-block--full" style="margin-top: 2.5rem;">
      <div class="origin-card">
        <div class="origin-card-inner">
          <!-- Childhood photo -->
          <div class="origin-photo-wrap">
            <img
              src="/devon-young.jpg"
              alt="Devon, young — already wearing sunglasses"
              class="origin-photo"
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Story text -->
          <div>
            <span class="origin-label">Origin</span>
            <p class="font-inter text-rk-muted leading-relaxed" style="font-size: 1.05rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">
              The name goes back further than the business. Reality Knights started as a
              content crew — Devon and a friend making video content with a simple tagline:
              <em class="text-rk-glow font-medium not-italic">"Reality Knights because Reality Bites."</em>
              A nod to nightlife, a claim to being gentlemen about it. The name stuck.
              The ambition grew.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 280px 1fr;
    gap: 3.5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-photo-col {
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-photo-wrap {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    display: block;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .about-photo-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -2px;
    border-radius: 1.125rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4, #7C3AED);
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.5;
    filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .about-text-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    padding-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .about-block--full {
    grid-column: 1 / -1;
  }

  .about-accent-bar {
    width: 2.5rem;
    height: 3px;
    border-radius: 2px;
  }

  .origin-card {
    position: relative;
    background: #13131C;
    border: 1px solid #1E1E2E;
    border-left: 3px solid #7C3AED;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
  }

  .origin-card-inner {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.75rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .origin-photo-wrap {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .origin-photo {
    width: 90px;
    height: 110px;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
    filter: sepia(20%) contrast(1.05);
  }

  .origin-label {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #7C3AED;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .about-photo-col {
      max-width: 220px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .origin-card-inner {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.25rem;
    }

    .origin-photo {
      width: 70px;
      height: 85px;
    }
  }
</style>
